<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-848] PageDrawer does not take the full CropBox into account</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-848</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A client sent me a PDF which was basically a double-sided page of which only the right side was shown by the CropBox. But PDFBox displayed the left side in the PDFReader. I&apos;ve created a minimal test case with FOP and a Hex Editor showing the problem. It seems as if the PageDrawer doesn&apos;t take the full CropBox information into account when painting the page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
