                            <comment id="12916900" author="jeremias@apache.org" created="Fri, 1 Oct 2010 14:41:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a patch for this issue. I&apos;d like a second pair of eyes before applying this. Also, because PDFBox has a problem with the TJ operator generated by FOP with a base 14 font active. But that&apos;s a different issue. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12916906" author="lehmi" created="Fri, 1 Oct 2010 14:59:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What version are you using? The latest trunk version (1003396) includes a fix for the extraction/rendering of text and one of the key issues was the handling of the TJ operator. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-828&quot; title=&quot;Spaces dissapear and text is shifted left&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-828&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-828&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for further details. &lt;br/&gt;
After applying your proposed patch to the latest trunk everything seems to be fine. I can&apos;t see any problem with the TJ operator. I&apos;m attaching the result of PDFToImage.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12917507" author="jeremias@apache.org" created="Mon, 4 Oct 2010 07:47:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch applied. &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1004135&amp;amp;view=rev&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1004135&amp;amp;view=rev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks for the review, Andreas! I&apos;ll reply on the second issue on-list.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
